    <segment id="1" parent="11" relname="preparation">Great comments on intuitiveness P40.</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="3" relname="volitional-cause">I buy a lot of books from Amazon.com,</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="13" relname="span">and sometimes I&apos;m amazed at how they can gage what else I like.</segment>
